sentences: Jay Rosen (born November 20, 1961) is an American jazz drummer.
He began an association with the CIMP label in 1996, and has also recorded for Cadence).

231 Since 1998, Rosen has performed with Joe McPhee and Dominic Duval in Trio X.: 360  In 2000, he joined Cosmosomatics, a quartet with saxophonists Sonny Simmons and Michael Marcus and bassist William Parker.: 114
